        <item>
            <title>英超曼城推生成式 AI 球衣设计工具，举行比赛优胜作品可成 26/27 球季第三球衣</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/mancity-puma-launched-genai-kit-design-platform/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mancity-puma-launched-genai-kit-design-platform</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/mancity-puma-launched-genai-kit-design-platform/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 14:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[epl]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gen AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Manchester City]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PUMA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[曼城]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280171</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>如果有睇英超的球迷应该都知道，班霸曼城随著伤兵累累，近期的走势确实不太理想。不过今日的消息，相信会令不少曼城支持者感到兴奋！曼城宣布与运动品牌 PUMA 合作推出全新的生成式 AI 平台，让全球球迷可以透过它设计具个人风格的球衣，设计后更可参加比赛，优胜者甚至会成为 2026/27 球季的第三球衣，确实十分吸引！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次这个生成式 AI 球衣设计平台，是由 DEEPOBJECTS 开发，而在设计平台上，球迷只需要输入电邮登记就可以获得 16 个 credits，之后输入球衣风格的关键字、球衣设计风格及球衣内含的颜色，再按下「Generate」就可以在半分钟左右生成具个人风格的球衣，系统亦会有 4 款效果供用家进行微调，之后再递交作品即可，用家亦可下载自己设计的球衣图档作收藏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_003.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_004.jpg 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_005.jpg 1213w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_006.jpg 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_008.jpg 1213w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mancityai_010.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>笔者自己亦试过，如果快的话只需 5 分钟已可递交一份作品，而且整个过程十分流畅，即使没有设计天分的笔者亦可设计出颇具型格的球衣。大家不妨自己试玩一下吧？万一赢了随时艾达臣、夏兰特可能会穿著你设计的球衣在球场上驰骋呢！</p><p>来源：<a href="https://aicreator.puma.com/">曼城</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/12/10/mancity-puma-launched-genai-kit-design-platform/life-tech/">英超曼城推生成式 AI 球衣设计工具，举行比赛优胜作品可成 26/27 球季第三球衣</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
