                <![CDATA[<p>近日中国深圳市宝安区首批拥有独立路权的非机动车（港称：电动可移动工具）示范道路正式完工，并已投入使用。这批示范道路有望为宝安电动可移动工具建立标准，为电动可移动工具驾驶者提供路权支援，提升骑行体验和安全性。</p><p>示范道路包括新安六路、湖滨西路、宝民二路和沙松路等，新安六路设置了 1,000 米长的「非机动车道」，两侧各有 3 米宽的护栏隔离，保障骑行安全。湖滨西路压缩机动车道后，新增 900 米长、2 米宽的「非机动车道」，缓解步行者和骑行者之间的冲突。宝民二路取消 54 个停车位，清理违停车辆后，设置 865 米长、2.5 米宽的「非机动车道」。沙松路将双向 4 车道调整为双向 2 车道，新增 1,500 米长、2.5 米宽的「非机动车道」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030-694x577.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="577" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030-694x577.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015030.jpg 982w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新安六路「非机动车道路」总长 1,000 米（图片来源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">腾讯网</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded8310d.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的新安六路，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a-694x408.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a-694x408.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded6112a.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造后新安六路「非机动车道路」，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230-684x580.jpg" alt="" width="684" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230-684x580.jpg 684w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015230.jpg 976w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 684px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲湖滨西路「非机动车道路」总长 900 米（图片来源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">腾讯网</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7-694x502.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="502" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7-694x502.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9deda0cf7.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的湖滨西路，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9ded92cfc.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造后湖滨西路「非机动车道路」，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610-694x539.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="539" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610-694x539.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015610.jpg 979w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲宝民二路「非机动车道路」总长 865 米（图片来源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">腾讯网</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a-694x520.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a-694x520.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedc642a.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造前的宝民二路，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img674f9dedb2155.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲改造后宝民二路「非机动车道路」，图片来源：<a href="https://www.baoanone.com/content173554.html">宝安湾</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714-677x580.jpg" alt="" width="677" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714-677x580.jpg 677w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024121015714.jpg 984w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 677px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲沙松路「非机动车道路」总长 1,500 米（图片来源：<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">腾讯网</a>）</p><p>中国深圳市宝安区自 2019 年开始加快「非机动车道」建设，2024 年新增 40 公里独立式「非机动车道」，以建立功能清晰、布局合理、连续安全的舒适「非机动车道」网络，减少电动可移动工具与城市交通系统的冲突，推动中国深圳市绿色出行和智慧城市发展。</p><p>除了增设「非机动车道」，中国深圳亦简化了电动可移动工具「以旧换新」政策，目前无须再填写大量表格，仅需办理「报废证明」即可换新电动可移动工具。另外中国深圳全部销售商家（包括个体工商户）亦可销售电动可移动工具，以方便中国深圳市民。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/833707215_121384220">搜狐</a>、<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241207A07Y2400">QQ News</a>、<a href="https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20241205A00ZON00">QQ News</a></p><div class="html-div xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1h91t0o xkh2ocl x78zum5 xdt5ytf x13a6bvl x193iq5w x1iyjqo2 x1eb86dx" role="presentation"></div><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========<br /><b>
